cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MA 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with fleet management for autonomous vehicles in a Mobility on Demand (MOD) system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a Bayesian framework to model customer demand and an exploration planner to route MOD vehicles. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques to learn and utilize customer demand. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling a fleet of autonomous vehicles in response to customer demand. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is also relevant as the paper deals with managing a fleet of autonomous vehicles to serve multiple customers.
